name: Parasite
description: A poor family schemes to become employed by a wealthy family by infiltrating their household.

name: The Handmaiden
description: A woman is hired as a handmaiden to a Japanese heiress, but secretly she is involved in a plot to defraud her.

name: Oldboy
description: After being kidnapped and imprisoned for fifteen years, Oh Dae-Su is released, only to find that he must find his captor in five days.

name: Train to Busan
description: While a zombie outbreak suddenly breaks out in South Korea, passengers struggle to survive on the train from Seoul to Busan.

name: Memories of Murder
description: In a small Korean province in 1986, two detectives struggle to catch a serial killer who is randomly murdering women.

name: Spirited Away
description: During her family's move to the suburbs, a sullen 10-year-old girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, witches, and spirits.

name: Rashomon
description: The rape of a bride and the murder of her samurai husband are recalled from the perspectives of a bandit, the bride, the samurai's ghost and a woodcutter.

name: Akira
description: A biker gang leader and his friend get involved in a violent struggle against a government project that is developing psychic weapons.

name: Your Name.
description: Two teenagers share a profound, magical connection upon discovering they are swapping bodies.

name: Princess Mononoke
description: On a journey to find the cure for a demonic curse, a young warrior gets caught up in a battle between the gods of the forest and the humans who want to use its resources.

name: Amlie
description: Amlie is an innocent and naive girl in Paris with her own sense of justice.

name: The Intouchables
description: After he becomes a quadriplegic from a paragliding accident, an aristocrat hires a young man from the projects to be his caregiver.

name: La La Land
description: While navigating their careers in Los Angeles, a pianist and an actress fall in love while attempting to reconcile their aspirations for the future.

name: Portrait of a Lady on Fire
description: On an isolated island in Brittany at the end of the eighteenth century, a young painter is commissioned to paint the wedding portrait of a reluctant bride-to-be.

name: Cyrano de Bergerac
description: Cyrano, a cadet in the French Army, is a brilliant duelist and wordsmith who is deeply in love with his cousin Roxane.

name: The Shawshank Redemption
description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

name: The Dark Knight
description: When the menace known as the Joker emerges from his mysterious past, he wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham.

name: Forrest Gump
description: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the events of Vietnam, Watergate, and other history unfold through the perspective of an Alabama man with an IQ of 75.

name: Inception
description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.

name: Fight Club
description: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soap maker form an underground fight club that evolves into much more.
